::Feline::

She kept walking down the hall.  She stopped just outside the hallway 
to the brig.  She was standing infront of an old storage bin with bot 
parts tossed in it.  She smiled,"YES! The mother load!"

She started picking out circuit boards and wires, arm joints, leg 
joints,  spare optical sencsors and stuff.  she hummed to herself as 
she went rummaging through the bin.  A box of bolts and connectors 
fell to the floor with a bang.  She frowned at her klutziness and 
picked it up.  She kept looking for other parts she might need.
